* Temminck, ut supra; Dobson, Cat. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[2163,2322,5333,5400]" pageId="51" pageNumber="126">Chir</emphasis>
. Brit. Mus. (1878) p. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[3143,3277,5333,5400]" pageId="51" pageNumber="126">117</emphasis>
